        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Starts (1) frame-grabbing loop and (2) message loop<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Function passed as an argument must implement common OCV reading frames pattern (see <ref refid="d8/dfe/classcv_1_1VideoCapture" kindref="compound">cv::VideoCapture</ref> documentation) AND call cv::winrt_imgshow().</para></listitem><listitem><para>Message processing loop required to overcome WinRT container and type conversion restrictions. OCV provides default implementation Here is how the class can be used: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">void cvMain()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    Mat frame;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    VideoCapture cam;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    cam.open(0);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    while (1)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    {</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">        cam &gt;&gt; frame;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">        // don&apos;t reprocess the same frame again</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">        if (!cam.grab()) continue;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">        // your processing logic goes here</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">        // obligatory step to get XAML image component updated</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">        winrt_imshow();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    }</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">MainPage::MainPage()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    InitializeComponent();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    cv::winrt_setFrameContainer(cvImage);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">    cv::winrt_startMessageLoop(cvMain);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para></listitem></orderedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
